WEBVTT

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:02.616
This is the second point, very simple.

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:04.456
Look at other sites.

00:04:04.480 --> 00:04:07.096
Check out alternative news sources.

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:12.536
Google names, addresses,
license plates, experts and authors.

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:14.160
Don't just believe, check.

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:18.800
It's the only way
to stop this culture of fake news.

00:04:19.640 --> 00:04:23.136
This information warfare
is not only about fake news.

00:04:23.160 --> 00:04:25.760
Our society depends on trust:

00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:28.696
trust in our institutions,

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:30.096
in science,